flights to europe and other points to make sure that their people 
are protected 
airlines and travel agents surveyed in bahrain said flights to 
britain the philippines india and egypt were fully booked from 
about jan 4 through jan 15 with long waiting lists in some 
cases the lists are so long theyve been closed off 
i wouldnt say theres panic but concern is spreading 
horsley said 
