system and directed the passage of legislation to bring order to 
the states haphazard growth 
he kept a lid on taxes for his first term making good on a 
campaign promise that helped put him into office but he didnt 
renew the notax pledge to win reelection in 1986 and three years 
later presided over the largest tax increase in state history 
now the state is teetering on the edge of a recessioninduced 
financial slide 
environmental issues were particularly troublesome for harris 
