had agreed to permit the appearance of an opposition newspaper 
twice a week a major opposition demand stani said the paper 
democratic renaissance would would be published this week there 
was no government confirmation that permission had been granted 
student protests over conditions in slumlike dormitories 
swelled two weeks ago into demands for democracy and helped force 
the ruling communists to permit other parties 
