rally but reporters saw no arrests or clashes between police and 
demonstrators 
three trucks with helmeted riot police swiftly appeared when 
chanting crowds leaving the rally site got to central skanderbeg 
square about a mile away but the demonstrators moved on when 
ordered to do so by police 
